includes.contactNote: This beautiful brand new never lived in carriage home at White Springs at Providence is ready to move right in! The front portico provides a warm welcome as you enter the foyer area that is opened to a beautiful formal dining with chair rail and chandelier.   There is a powder room and laundry area to the left of the entrance as well as a large coat closet.   The first floor leads into the large kitchen and living room area with ample windows full natural light and vaulted ceilings. The gourmet kitchen comes with huge center island/breakfast bar, 42" cabinets, granite countertops, 5 burner gas cooktop, large custom sink, wall oven, pantry closet, microwave, dishwasher, garbage disposal, ceramic tile backsplash, vaulted ceiling, recessed lighting and all stainless steel appliances. The huge living room comes with recessed lighting and a gas fireplace for cozy fall/winter nights.  This home comes with an amazing first floor master and ensuite.  Master has tray ceilings and a enormous walk in closet right off the master bath.  The ensuite has soaking tub, shower, double vanity sink, and water closet.  The first floor is completed by a large deck off the back house for a nice scenic view, great for entertaining on summer days.  The second comes with a great open loft area hallway.  This space could be used for TV area or office.  The second floor comes with 3 generous size bedrooms all with deep closets.  The back bedroom has its own bathroom and could be considered a second master.  The hallway bathroom comes with a double sink to accommodate multiple users. House is equipped with high tech security system and monitors every access point of home. HOA covers roof. This is a lifestyle community which has a clubhouse with social rooms and fitness level, resort style outdoor pool, tennis and bocce courts. Walking trails and sidewalks with proximity to shopping outlets including Wegmans, dine in theater and highway access."

includes.contactNote: Welcome to this spectacular End-Unit Carriage home with 2,879 sq ft of living space, offering 4 bedrooms & 3.5 baths on a premium corner lot. Lovingly cared for by its original owners, this stunning Hengrave Elite floorplan shows like a model home with over $74K of builder upgrades and an additional $20K upgrades by the seller (Detailed list of upgrades is available through your agent). Located in the desirable White Springs at Providence in the Manor Collection (no age restriction), this house has a private side entrance to an open foyer & formal Dining Room with wainscoting and double crown molding trim. Gleaming Cherry Oak Hardwood flooring in the entire 1st floor living space. With an open concept floorplan, the bright & airy Great Room has many large windows, a tile surround gas fireplace, vaulted ceiling, upgraded blinds and adjoins the kitchen. The beautiful Gourmet Kitchen boasts of 42-inch maple custom cabinets, soft close drawers, accented tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances, double sink with upgraded disposal, a 4-burner downdraft gas cooking range, wall-mounted microwave & oven range, huge extended island & granite countertops. The glass door from the Great Room leads to a large expanded maintenance free Trex Deck 20 ft X 24 ft.  Off the Great Room is the luxurious 1st floor Master Suite with a custom retreat style Master Bathroom that offers an enormous tiled shower, double vanity, whirlpool tub & leads to a walk in closet. 1st floor also has a beautiful half bath & a laundry room with extra shelving & a laundry rack. Stairs to the 2nd floor lead to an open yet cozy loft area, two spacious bedrooms with walk-in closets & a full bathroom in the hallway. An additional 4th bedroom has an attached private full bath. All bedroom closets have custom shelving done by Closets by Design & every room has a high-end ceiling fan. House offers an added convenience of two laundry rooms - one on the 1st floor exclusively for the Master Bedroom & the other one on the 2nd floor serving the three bedrooms upstairs. The house has built-in CAT 6 wiring throughout, in addition to the internal home theater wiring in the Great Room. There is a full unfinished basement & an expanded Two Car attached Garage with a Two Car driveway. Enjoy all the excellent amenities of the community like the clubhouse, fitness room, tennis court & swimming pool. Minutes from Wegmans, Movie Tavern & Providence Town Center. Located in the sought after Springford school district.
